Text: Kevin Alas of NLEX battles for the lose ball against LA Revila of Mahindra during a PBA Commissioner’s Cup game at the Araneta Coliseum on Friday. PHOTO BY CZEASAR DANCEL The Mahindra Enforcers defeated the NLEX Road Warriors, 106-99, to record their third win in the Philippine Basketball Association (PBA) Commissioner’s Cup 2016 at the Smart-Araneta Coliseum on Friday.
